   339→
   340→/**
   341→ * Workflow 4: Performance Optimization Pipeline
   342→ *
   343→ * End-to-end performance optimization:
   344→ * 1. Research Agent: Research optimization techniques
   345→ * 2. Coding Agent: Profile and identify bottlenecks
